{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01QwuQbACH8PqHHa49qtYE8W","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0128XeyHw3aqiJfi5zEa88Bn","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/home/jorgecevallos/Documents/web-video/.ralph-tui/progress.md","old_string":"  - Tailwind v4 arbitrary values like `grid-rows-[0fr]` work seamlessly for this pattern\n  - `divide-y divide-border` on the container cleanly handles separator lines between accordion items\n---","new_string":"  - Tailwind v4 arbitrary values like `grid-rows-[0fr]` work seamlessly for this pattern\n  - `divide-y divide-border` on the container cleanly handles separator lines between accordion items\n---\n\n## 2026-02-17 - web-video-l39.8\n- Created Footer component (`components/Footer.tsx`) with minimalist design\n- Footer includes dynamic copyright year, privacy and contact links\n- Uses `border-t border-border` and `bg-surface/50` for subtle visual separation\n- Responsive layout: stacked on mobile, horizontal on desktop (`sm:flex-row`)\n- Updated `app/page.tsx` to render Footer outside `<main>` using a fragment wrapper\n- **Files changed:**\n  - `components/Footer.tsx` - New footer component\n  - `app/page.tsx` - Added Footer import and rendering, wrapped in fragment\n- **Learnings:**\n  - `bg-surface/50` (opacity modifier) creates a subtle background that differentiates the footer from the main content without being too prominent\n  - Footer is placed outside `<main>` for semantic HTML — it's a sibling, not a child of main content\n---"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":192,"cache_read_input_tokens":29332,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":192},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8892a807-4082-49e8